      "content_html": "<p>2025 gaya. Apne peechhe chhod gaya ek changed real estate landscape. 2026 mein invest karne se pehle yeh 7 trends samajhna zaroori hai.</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Trend 1 — Luxury is the New Mid-Segment:</strong> ₹1.25 Cr+ homes ka share 2021 mein 11% tha, ab 27%. Premium buyer strong hai.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 2 — Domestic Capital Dominance:</strong> Foreign investment 75% gira. Domestic investors ne 75% market capture kiya. Stability ka sign.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 3 — Rental Market Surge:</strong> Urban rents 6-8% badhe in 2026. Middle class affordability squeeze rentals ko long-term strong banata hai.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 4 — Tier-2 Price Discovery:</strong> Jaipur +65%, Guntur +51%, Indore +20%. Raipur jaisi cities still ₹3,000-4,000/sq ft — next discovery cycle mein.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 5 — Infrastructure-Led Appreciation:</strong> MIHAN Nagpur, Naya Raipur, Ring Roads — sarkaar ka infra investment directly land value badhata hai.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 6 — RERA Non-Negotiable:</strong> Unregistered project mein koi nahi ja raha. RERA-compliant developers win kar rahe hain.</li>\n      <li><strong>Trend 7 — Alternative Assets Rise:</strong> SM-REITs, co-living, warehousing — retail investors ke liye naye avenues.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Key takeaway:</strong> Post-2025 real estate is not one market. It's 15 different markets. Trends samjho, then city, asset aur time choose karo.</p>",
