      "description": "2021 mein ₹40 lakh wala segment king tha. 2025 mein ₹1.25 Cr+ segment 27% market share tha. Yeh kya hua? Aur iska aap par kya impact hai? Luxury Segment Kyun Boom Kar Raha Hai Post-COVID lifestyle upg...",
      "content_html": "<p>2021 mein ₹40 lakh wala segment king tha. 2025 mein ₹1.25 Cr+ segment 27% market share tha. Yeh kya hua? Aur iska aap par kya impact hai?</p>\n    <h3>Luxury Segment Kyun Boom Kar Raha Hai</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Post-COVID lifestyle upgrades — bigger space, better amenities</li>\n      <li>NRI purchasing power — dollar-strong buyers</li>\n      <li>Upper-middle class income growth outpacing inflation</li>\n      <li>Developers ne supply shift kiya — affordable mein margins thin hain</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Affordable Housing Kahan Hai</h3>\n    <p>Affordable housing squeezed out ho rahi hai metros mein. ₹40-60 lakh budget ke buyers increasingly difficult position mein hain — metro mein sahi property nahi milti, periphery mein connectivity nahi.</p>\n    <p>Yahi wajah hai Tier-2 cities boom ho rahi hain. Raipur mein ₹35-45 lakh mein proper 2BHK milti hai gated community mein. Indore mein ₹50-70 lakh mein quality product.</p>\n    <h3>Future mein Kaun Jeetega</h3>\n    <p>Dono segments ka role hai. Luxury metros mein strong rahega. Affordable housing ka story Tier-2 aur Tier-3 cities mein likhega. Smart investor dono pe nazar rakhta hai — aur sahi city choose karta hai.</p>\n    <p><strong>Key insight:</strong> Agar aapka budget ₹50 lakh tak hai, metro mein luxury sirf dream hai. Tier-2 mein yeh reality ban sakti hai — aur better ROI ke saath.</p>",
      "content_text": "2021 mein ₹40 lakh wala segment king tha. 2025 mein ₹1.25 Cr+ segment 27% market share tha. Yeh kya hua? Aur iska aap par kya impact hai? Luxury Segment Kyun Boom Kar Raha Hai Post-COVID lifestyle upgrades — bigger space, better amenities NRI purchasing power — dollar-strong buyers Upper-middle class income growth outpacing inflation Developers ne supply shift kiya — affordable mein margins thin hain Affordable Housing Kahan Hai Affordable housing squeezed out ho rahi hai metros mein. ₹40-60 lakh budget ke buyers increasingly difficult position mein hain — metro mein sahi property nahi milti, periphery mein connectivity nahi. Yahi wajah hai Tier-2 cities boom ho rahi hain. Raipur mein ₹35-45 lakh mein proper 2BHK milti hai gated community mein. Indore mein ₹50-70 lakh mein quality product. Future mein Kaun Jeetega Dono segments ka role hai. Luxury metros mein strong rahega. Affordable housing ka story Tier-2 aur Tier-3 cities mein likhega. Smart investor dono pe nazar rakhta hai — aur sahi city choose karta hai. Key insight: Agar aapka budget ₹50 lakh tak hai, metro mein luxury sirf dream hai. Tier-2 mein yeh reality ban sakti hai — aur better ROI ke saath.",
