      "description": "Yeh sawaal aaj har investor ke dimag mein hai. Wait karein ya ab enter karein? Data ke basis par seedha jawab dete hain. 2026 mein Enter Karne ke Reasons (For) Home loan rates 7% ke paas — multi-year ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Yeh sawaal aaj har investor ke dimag mein hai. Wait karein ya ab enter karein? Data ke basis par seedha jawab dete hain.</p>\n    <h3>2026 mein Enter Karne ke Reasons (For)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Home loan rates 7% ke paas — multi-year low EMIs</li>\n      <li>Developers negotiable hain — inventory pressure mein discount milta hai</li>\n      <li>Domestic capital strong hai — India ka real estate India-driven</li>\n      <li>Tier-2 cities abhi pre-peak stage par hain</li>\n      <li>Long-term 9.6% CAGR market projection intact</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Wait Karne ke Reasons (Against)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Metro micro-markets mein aur correction possible (10-25%)</li>\n      <li>Global uncertainty short-term mein persist kar sakti hai</li>\n      <li>Job market mein kuch softness dikhti hai IT sector mein</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Verdict</h3>\n    <p>Agar target Tier-2 city hai, RERA-verified project hai, aur 3-5 saal ka horizon hai — <strong>2026 ek strong entry year hai.</strong></p>\n    <p>Agar metro premium luxury property ki baat hai, bina clear rental yield ke — wait ya very carefully due diligence karo.</p>\n    <p><strong>Remember:</strong> \"Perfect time\" kabhi nahi aata. Best time woh hota hai jab fundamentals strong hon aur sentiment cautious ho. 2026 mein dono conditions hain — Tier-2 ke liye.</p>",
      "content_text": "Yeh sawaal aaj har investor ke dimag mein hai. Wait karein ya ab enter karein? Data ke basis par seedha jawab dete hain. 2026 mein Enter Karne ke Reasons (For) Home loan rates 7% ke paas — multi-year low EMIs Developers negotiable hain — inventory pressure mein discount milta hai Domestic capital strong hai — India ka real estate India-driven Tier-2 cities abhi pre-peak stage par hain Long-term 9.6% CAGR market projection intact Wait Karne ke Reasons (Against) Metro micro-markets mein aur correction possible (10-25%) Global uncertainty short-term mein persist kar sakti hai Job market mein kuch softness dikhti hai IT sector mein Verdict Agar target Tier-2 city hai, RERA-verified project hai, aur 3-5 saal ka horizon hai — 2026 ek strong entry year hai. Agar metro premium luxury property ki baat hai, bina clear rental yield ke — wait ya very carefully due diligence karo. Remember: \"Perfect time\" kabhi nahi aata. Best time woh hota hai jab fundamentals strong hon aur sentiment cautious ho. 2026 mein dono conditions hain — Tier-2 ke liye.",
