      "tags": [
        "Bubble Analysis",
        "Opportunity"
      ],
      "description": "Kuch log keh rahe hain \"bubble aane wala hai.\" Kuch log keh rahe hain \"greatest opportunity of the decade.\" Dono wrong ya dono right? Data se seedha baat karte hain. Bubble Signs (Jo Hain) Mumbai, Gur...",
      "content_html": "<p>Kuch log keh rahe hain \"bubble aane wala hai.\" Kuch log keh rahe hain \"greatest opportunity of the decade.\" Dono wrong ya dono right? Data se seedha baat karte hain.</p>\n    <h3>Bubble Signs (Jo Hain)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Mumbai, Gurgaon mein prices income se aage nikal gayi</li>\n      <li>Unsold inventory 5.77 lakh units — slowly rising</li>\n      <li>Post-COVID price jump 20-35% in many cities</li>\n      <li>Foreign investment 75% gira Q1 2026 mein</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Opportunity Signs (Jo Bhi Hain)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>India ka urbanisation engine chal raha hai — 600 million urban by 2036</li>\n      <li>Tier-2 cities still affordable — Raipur ₹3,810/sq ft</li>\n      <li>RERA ne market ko transparent banaya — 2008 jaisi toxic exposure nahi</li>\n      <li>Domestic demand floor strong — end-user market</li>\n      <li>Market projected to reach $927B by 2031</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Honest Assessment</h3>\n    <p>Select metro micro-markets mein — <strong>bubble risk real hai.</strong> Tier-2 early-stage cities mein — <strong>opportunity real hai.</strong> Yeh ek market nahi, 20 markets hain — har ek ko alag se judge karna hoga.</p>\n    <p><strong>Smart move:</strong> Bubble wali cities se dur raho. Opportunity wali cities identify karo — aur data ke saath enter karo.</p>",
      "content_text": "Kuch log keh rahe hain \"bubble aane wala hai.\" Kuch log keh rahe hain \"greatest opportunity of the decade.\" Dono wrong ya dono right? Data se seedha baat karte hain. Bubble Signs (Jo Hain) Mumbai, Gurgaon mein prices income se aage nikal gayi Unsold inventory 5.77 lakh units — slowly rising Post-COVID price jump 20-35% in many cities Foreign investment 75% gira Q1 2026 mein Opportunity Signs (Jo Bhi Hain) India ka urbanisation engine chal raha hai — 600 million urban by 2036 Tier-2 cities still affordable — Raipur ₹3,810/sq ft RERA ne market ko transparent banaya — 2008 jaisi toxic exposure nahi Domestic demand floor strong — end-user market Market projected to reach $927B by 2031 Honest Assessment Select metro micro-markets mein — bubble risk real hai. Tier-2 early-stage cities mein — opportunity real hai. Yeh ek market nahi, 20 markets hain — har ek ko alag se judge karna hoga. Smart move: Bubble wali cities se dur raho. Opportunity wali cities identify karo — aur data ke saath enter karo.",
