      "description": "Bahut log wait kar rahe hain — \"property prices girengi toh main khareedunga.\" Kya yeh strategy sahi hai? Truth kya hai? Nationally — Girana Unlikely RBI ka RESIDEX House Price Index 2025 mein 3.58% y...",
      "content_html": "<p>Bahut log wait kar rahe hain — \"property prices girengi toh main khareedunga.\" Kya yeh strategy sahi hai? Truth kya hai?</p>\n    <h3>Nationally — Girana Unlikely</h3>\n    <p>RBI ka RESIDEX House Price Index 2025 mein 3.58% year-on-year badha. Structural demand — 600 million urban population by 2036, nuclear families, urbanisation — yeh floor provide karta hai jo broad collapse ko prevent karta hai.</p>\n    <h3>Locally — Haan, Corrections Possible</h3>\n    <p>Mumbai ke certain premium zones: 10-20% correction possible. Gurgaon ke overpriced sectors: selective drops ho sakte hain. Bengaluru fringe: Demand softness.</p>\n    <h3>Tier-2 Cities — Very Unlikely to Fall</h3>\n    <p>Raipur, Nagpur, Indore — inki price discovery abhi shuru hai. Supply controlled hai. Demand organic hai. Yahan significant giraawat ka koi structural reason nahi hai.</p>\n    <h3>Waiting Game Ka Risk</h3>\n    <p>Jo log \"prices girengi\" wait karte hain, unka real enemy sirf prices nahi — woh lost opportunity bhi hai. Agar koi property ₹50L se ₹45L aaye (10% correction), lekin aapka rent 4 saal mein ₹8L de chuka ho — kya wait sahi tha?</p>\n    <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Wait karo agar overheated metro mein speculative buy soch rahe ho. Tier-2 early-stage mein wait karna cost aapko pad sakta hai.</p>",
      "content_text": "Bahut log wait kar rahe hain — \"property prices girengi toh main khareedunga.\" Kya yeh strategy sahi hai? Truth kya hai? Nationally — Girana Unlikely RBI ka RESIDEX House Price Index 2025 mein 3.58% year-on-year badha. Structural demand — 600 million urban population by 2036, nuclear families, urbanisation — yeh floor provide karta hai jo broad collapse ko prevent karta hai. Locally — Haan, Corrections Possible Mumbai ke certain premium zones: 10-20% correction possible. Gurgaon ke overpriced sectors: selective drops ho sakte hain. Bengaluru fringe: Demand softness. Tier-2 Cities — Very Unlikely to Fall Raipur, Nagpur, Indore — inki price discovery abhi shuru hai. Supply controlled hai. Demand organic hai. Yahan significant giraawat ka koi structural reason nahi hai. Waiting Game Ka Risk Jo log \"prices girengi\" wait karte hain, unka real enemy sirf prices nahi — woh lost opportunity bhi hai. Agar koi property ₹50L se ₹45L aaye (10% correction), lekin aapka rent 4 saal mein ₹8L de chuka ho — kya wait sahi tha? Strategy: Wait karo agar overheated metro mein speculative buy soch rahe ho. Tier-2 early-stage mein wait karna cost aapko pad sakta hai.",
