      img: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599423300746-b62533397364?w=600&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60",
      "tags": [
        "Inflation Impact",
        "Economics"
      ],
      "description": "Jab inflation badh raha hota hai, log kehte hain \"property khareed lo, safe hai.\" Kya yeh sach hai? Aur kaise kaam karta hai yeh connection? Inflation aur Real Estate — The Basic Link Inflation matlab...",
      "content_html": "<p>Jab inflation badh raha hota hai, log kehte hain \"property khareed lo, safe hai.\" Kya yeh sach hai? Aur kaise kaam karta hai yeh connection?</p>\n    <h3>Inflation aur Real Estate — The Basic Link</h3>\n    <p>Inflation matlab money ki purchasing power ghaat rahi hai. ₹100 aaj jo khareed sakta hai, woh 5 saal baad ₹80 ki value ka hoga. Real assets — land, property — ki inherent value nahi ghatti. Isliye property inflation hedge ka kaam karti hai.</p>\n    <h3>3 Ways Inflation Pushes Property Prices</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Construction cost inflation:</strong> Steel, cement, labour cost badha = naye projects costly = existing properties ki value badhi</li>\n      <li><strong>Rental income inflation:</strong> Rents typically rise with or above inflation — rental property ka income stream protected</li>\n      <li><strong>Alternative asset comparison:</strong> High inflation mein bank FD real return negative ho jaata hai — people move to hard assets</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>But Risk Bhi Hai</h3>\n    <p>Agar central bank inflation rokne ke liye rates bahut badha de, to home loan EMIs badh jaati hain — demand gir sakti hai short-term mein.</p>\n    <h3>2026 Context</h3>\n    <p>RBI ne rates cut kiye hain — inflation controlled hai. Yeh goldilocks scenario hai: moderate inflation (property value supports), low rates (affordable EMIs). Ideal buying window.</p>",
      "content_text": "Jab inflation badh raha hota hai, log kehte hain \"property khareed lo, safe hai.\" Kya yeh sach hai? Aur kaise kaam karta hai yeh connection? Inflation aur Real Estate — The Basic Link Inflation matlab money ki purchasing power ghaat rahi hai. ₹100 aaj jo khareed sakta hai, woh 5 saal baad ₹80 ki value ka hoga. Real assets — land, property — ki inherent value nahi ghatti. Isliye property inflation hedge ka kaam karti hai. 3 Ways Inflation Pushes Property Prices Construction cost inflation: Steel, cement, labour cost badha = naye projects costly = existing properties ki value badhi Rental income inflation: Rents typically rise with or above inflation — rental property ka income stream protected Alternative asset comparison: High inflation mein bank FD real return negative ho jaata hai — people move to hard assets But Risk Bhi Hai Agar central bank inflation rokne ke liye rates bahut badha de, to home loan EMIs badh jaati hain — demand gir sakti hai short-term mein. 2026 Context RBI ne rates cut kiye hain — inflation controlled hai. Yeh goldilocks scenario hai: moderate inflation (property value supports), low rates (affordable EMIs). Ideal buying window.",
