      "tags": [
        "Govt Policies",
        "Policy Impact"
      ],
      "description": "Real estate sirf market forces se nahi chalta — government ka bhi bahut bada role hai. Kaun si policies property market ko sabse zyada affect karti hain? RERA — Game Changer Since 2016 Real Estate Reg...",
      "content_html": "<p>Real estate sirf market forces se nahi chalta — government ka bhi bahut bada role hai. Kaun si policies property market ko sabse zyada affect karti hain?</p>\n    <h3>RERA — Game Changer Since 2016</h3>\n    <p>Real Estate Regulatory Authority ne transparency layi. Escrow norms se buyer funds protected. Delivery delays ke liye penalty. Result: Trust badha, speculative launches ghate, quality developers survive kiye.</p>\n    <h3>Smart City Mission</h3>\n    <p>100 cities select kiye gaye. Raipur bhi isme hai. Infrastructure funding directly land value badhata hai. Smart city areas mein 20-40% premium already develop ho raha hai.</p>\n    <h3>PM Awas Yojana</h3>\n    <p>Affordable housing ke liye subsidy scheme. Millions of first-time buyers ko property market mein layi. Supply side bhi stimulate kiya.</p>\n    <h3>GST Impact</h3>\n    <p>Under-construction properties par GST (5% for affordable, 12% others) ek cost factor hai. GST rationalization proposals pending hain — agar aaya, affordability aur badhegi.</p>\n    <h3>Industrial Corridors</h3>\n    <p>Delhi-Mumbai, Mumbai-Ahmedabad, Chennai-Bengaluru — in corridors ke aas paas land values significantly badhe hain. Nagpur MIHAN isi category mein hai.</p>\n    <p><strong>Key learning:</strong> Government policy follow karo — wahan invest karo jahan government infrastructure daal rahi hai. Woh never-lose strategy hai long-term mein.</p>",
      "content_text": "Real estate sirf market forces se nahi chalta — government ka bhi bahut bada role hai. Kaun si policies property market ko sabse zyada affect karti hain? RERA — Game Changer Since 2016 Real Estate Regulatory Authority ne transparency layi. Escrow norms se buyer funds protected. Delivery delays ke liye penalty. Result: Trust badha, speculative launches ghate, quality developers survive kiye. Smart City Mission 100 cities select kiye gaye. Raipur bhi isme hai. Infrastructure funding directly land value badhata hai. Smart city areas mein 20-40% premium already develop ho raha hai. PM Awas Yojana Affordable housing ke liye subsidy scheme. Millions of first-time buyers ko property market mein layi. Supply side bhi stimulate kiya. GST Impact Under-construction properties par GST (5% for affordable, 12% others) ek cost factor hai. GST rationalization proposals pending hain — agar aaya, affordability aur badhegi. Industrial Corridors Delhi-Mumbai, Mumbai-Ahmedabad, Chennai-Bengaluru — in corridors ke aas paas land values significantly badhe hain. Nagpur MIHAN isi category mein hai. Key learning: Government policy follow karo — wahan invest karo jahan government infrastructure daal rahi hai. Woh never-lose strategy hai long-term mein.",
