      "description": "Raipur — Chhattisgarh ki capital — 2026 mein India ke most exciting emerging real estate markets mein se ek hai. Ek complete guide jo first-time buyers aur seasoned investors dono ke kaam aayegi. Mark...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur — Chhattisgarh ki capital — 2026 mein India ke most exciting emerging real estate markets mein se ek hai. Ek complete guide jo first-time buyers aur seasoned investors dono ke kaam aayegi.</p>\n    <h3>Market at a Glance</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Average price: ₹3,810/sq ft (PropEquity — lowest among top 30 Tier-2 cities)</li>\n      <li>2BHK range: ₹35-45 lakh (gated community)</li>\n      <li>3BHK range: ₹55-85 lakh</li>\n      <li>Best rental yields: Amanaka (7.1%), VIP Road (5.2%), Mahaveer Nagar (4.6%)</li>\n      <li>3-yr price growth: 14% stable (not frothy — good sign)</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Hot Micro-Markets</h3>\n    <p>Boria Kalan (164% 3-yr jump), Sejbahar (66.7%), Abhanpur (60%) — yeh fringe areas tezi se discover ho rahi hain. Naya Raipur corridor — planned development, institutional infrastructure — long-term biggest bet.</p>\n    <h3>Why Enter Now</h3>\n    <p>Raipur abhi pre-peak stage par hai. Infrastructure visible ho rahi hai, lekin prices ne abhi peak nahi kiya. Jab infrastructure complete hogi — aur investment se bhara Naya Raipur mature ho — tab prices jump karenge. Early buyers wo jump capitalize karenge.</p>\n    <p><strong>Always check:</strong> RERA registration on PCGRERA portal. Developer track record. Infrastructure timeline clarity.</p>",
      "content_text": "Raipur — Chhattisgarh ki capital — 2026 mein India ke most exciting emerging real estate markets mein se ek hai. Ek complete guide jo first-time buyers aur seasoned investors dono ke kaam aayegi. Market at a Glance Average price: ₹3,810/sq ft (PropEquity — lowest among top 30 Tier-2 cities) 2BHK range: ₹35-45 lakh (gated community) 3BHK range: ₹55-85 lakh Best rental yields: Amanaka (7.1%), VIP Road (5.2%), Mahaveer Nagar (4.6%) 3-yr price growth: 14% stable (not frothy — good sign) Hot Micro-Markets Boria Kalan (164% 3-yr jump), Sejbahar (66.7%), Abhanpur (60%) — yeh fringe areas tezi se discover ho rahi hain. Naya Raipur corridor — planned development, institutional infrastructure — long-term biggest bet. Why Enter Now Raipur abhi pre-peak stage par hai. Infrastructure visible ho rahi hai, lekin prices ne abhi peak nahi kiya. Jab infrastructure complete hogi — aur investment se bhara Naya Raipur mature ho — tab prices jump karenge. Early buyers wo jump capitalize karenge. Always check: RERA registration on PCGRERA portal. Developer track record. Infrastructure timeline clarity.",
