      "description": "Investors from Odisha, Jharkhand, Madhya Pradesh — sab Raipur ki taraf dekh rahe hain. Kyun? Kyunki Raipur ke paas woh sab kuch hai jo ek emerging investment hub mein hona chahiye. The 5 Growth Pillar...",
      "content_html": "<p>Investors from Odisha, Jharkhand, Madhya Pradesh — sab Raipur ki taraf dekh rahe hain. Kyun? Kyunki Raipur ke paas woh sab kuch hai jo ek emerging investment hub mein hona chahiye.</p>\n    <h3>The 5 Growth Pillars of Raipur</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Industry Base:</strong> Steel, cement, power — Chhattisgarh India ka industrial heartland hai. Professionals ki steady in-migration</li>\n      <li><strong>Government Capital:</strong> State capital = government jobs = stable salaried demand</li>\n      <li><strong>Smart City Funding:</strong> Raipur Smart City Mission mein included — civic upgrade ongoing</li>\n      <li><strong>Airport Connectivity:</strong> Swami Vivekananda Airport — domestic + some international routes</li>\n      <li><strong>Naya Raipur:</strong> India's one of the most planned greenfield cities — transforming the region</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Investor Interest Growing</h3>\n    <p>Investors from neighboring states increasingly looking at Raipur. Early-mover advantage still available. Once institutional developers fully arrive (which is starting), pricing will shift.</p>\n    <h3>The Indore Parallel</h3>\n    <p>5 saal pehle Indore mein log yahi pooch rahe the. \"Kya yahan invest karna sahi hai?\" Jo unhone kiya — unhe 20-40% appreciation mili. Raipur 2026 mein wahin khada hai. Woh window is still open.</p>",
      "content_text": "Investors from Odisha, Jharkhand, Madhya Pradesh — sab Raipur ki taraf dekh rahe hain. Kyun? Kyunki Raipur ke paas woh sab kuch hai jo ek emerging investment hub mein hona chahiye. The 5 Growth Pillars of Raipur Industry Base: Steel, cement, power — Chhattisgarh India ka industrial heartland hai. Professionals ki steady in-migration Government Capital: State capital = government jobs = stable salaried demand Smart City Funding: Raipur Smart City Mission mein included — civic upgrade ongoing Airport Connectivity: Swami Vivekananda Airport — domestic + some international routes Naya Raipur: India's one of the most planned greenfield cities — transforming the region Investor Interest Growing Investors from neighboring states increasingly looking at Raipur. Early-mover advantage still available. Once institutional developers fully arrive (which is starting), pricing will shift. The Indore Parallel 5 saal pehle Indore mein log yahi pooch rahe the. \"Kya yahan invest karna sahi hai?\" Jo unhone kiya — unhe 20-40% appreciation mili. Raipur 2026 mein wahin khada hai. Woh window is still open.",
