      "description": "Raipur mein \"kahan khareedein\" — yeh equally important sawaal hai. Sahi micro-market galat choice se 2x return de sakta hai. Yeh hain 2026 ke top 5 picks. 1. Naya Raipur Corridor Greenfield planned ci...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein \"kahan khareedein\" — yeh equally important sawaal hai. Sahi micro-market galat choice se 2x return de sakta hai. Yeh hain 2026 ke top 5 picks.</p>\n    <h3>1. Naya Raipur Corridor</h3>\n    <p>Greenfield planned city. Institutional infrastructure. Long-term highest appreciation potential. Best for patient investors (5-7 yr horizon). Naya Raipur (₹700/sq ft in some areas — massive upside).</p>\n    <h3>2. Sejbahar</h3>\n    <p>66.7% appreciation in 3 years. Residential demand strong. IT infrastructure nearby. Mid-range pricing. Good for mid-term investors.</p>\n    <h3>3. Amanaka</h3>\n    <p>Highest rental yield — 7.1%. For those wanting immediate rental income. Established area, good connectivity. Best for rental-income-first investors.</p>\n    <h3>4. VIP Road</h3>\n    <p>5.2% rental yield. Commercial and residential activity strong. Premium positioning. Good for commercial + residential mixed approach.</p>\n    <h3>5. Boria Kalan</h3>\n    <p>164.3% price appreciation in 3 years — highest in Raipur. Emerging area, still affordable. High-risk, high-reward. For investors comfortable with emerging micro-markets.</p>\n    <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Amanaka for yield now. Naya Raipur for appreciation later. Boria Kalan for aggressive upside bet. Diversify across 2-3 micro-markets if budget allows.</p>",
      "content_text": "Raipur mein \"kahan khareedein\" — yeh equally important sawaal hai. Sahi micro-market galat choice se 2x return de sakta hai. Yeh hain 2026 ke top 5 picks. 1. Naya Raipur Corridor Greenfield planned city. Institutional infrastructure. Long-term highest appreciation potential. Best for patient investors (5-7 yr horizon). Naya Raipur (₹700/sq ft in some areas — massive upside). 2. Sejbahar 66.7% appreciation in 3 years. Residential demand strong. IT infrastructure nearby. Mid-range pricing. Good for mid-term investors. 3. Amanaka Highest rental yield — 7.1%. For those wanting immediate rental income. Established area, good connectivity. Best for rental-income-first investors. 4. VIP Road 5.2% rental yield. Commercial and residential activity strong. Premium positioning. Good for commercial + residential mixed approach. 5. Boria Kalan 164.3% price appreciation in 3 years — highest in Raipur. Emerging area, still affordable. High-risk, high-reward. For investors comfortable with emerging micro-markets. Strategy: Amanaka for yield now. Naya Raipur for appreciation later. Boria Kalan for aggressive upside bet. Diversify across 2-3 micro-markets if budget allows.",
