      "description": "Raipur mein invest karna decide kar liya. Ab agla sawaal: Plot loon ya flat? Dono ke apne pros aur cons hain. Aapki situation ke hisaab se answer alag ho sakta hai. Plot — Kyun Lena Chahiye Land pure ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein invest karna decide kar liya. Ab agla sawaal: Plot loon ya flat? Dono ke apne pros aur cons hain. Aapki situation ke hisaab se answer alag ho sakta hai.</p>\n    <h3>Plot — Kyun Lena Chahiye</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Land pure appreciation — depreciation zero (unlike structure)</li>\n      <li>Flexibility — jab chahein banao, jitna chahein banao</li>\n      <li>Higher long-term upside — especially in emerging corridors</li>\n      <li>Lower maintenance cost — koi building maintenance nahi</li>\n      <li>Naya Raipur aur fringe areas mein best bet</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Plot — Risks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>No rental income until construction</li>\n      <li>Title verification crucial — koi bhi plot nahi chalega</li>\n      <li>Must be RERA-registered layout project</li>\n      <li>Longer liquidity timeline</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Flat — Kyun Lena Chahiye</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Immediate rental income possible</li>\n      <li>Ready-to-move options available</li>\n      <li>Lower entry in prime established areas</li>\n      <li>Better liquidity vs plot</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Flat — Risks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Building depreciates over time</li>\n      <li>Society maintenance charges</li>\n      <li>Developer quality matters hugely</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>2026 Raipur Recommendation</h3>\n    <p><strong>If rental income priority:</strong> Flat in Amanaka or VIP Road. <strong>If long-term appreciation priority:</strong> RERA-registered plot in Naya Raipur or Sejbahar corridor. <strong>Best combo:</strong> Flat for yield + Plot for growth — if budget allows split.</p>",
      "content_text": "Raipur mein invest karna decide kar liya. Ab agla sawaal: Plot loon ya flat? Dono ke apne pros aur cons hain. Aapki situation ke hisaab se answer alag ho sakta hai. Plot — Kyun Lena Chahiye Land pure appreciation — depreciation zero (unlike structure) Flexibility — jab chahein banao, jitna chahein banao Higher long-term upside — especially in emerging corridors Lower maintenance cost — koi building maintenance nahi Naya Raipur aur fringe areas mein best bet Plot — Risks No rental income until construction Title verification crucial — koi bhi plot nahi chalega Must be RERA-registered layout project Longer liquidity timeline Flat — Kyun Lena Chahiye Immediate rental income possible Ready-to-move options available Lower entry in prime established areas Better liquidity vs plot Flat — Risks Building depreciates over time Society maintenance charges Developer quality matters hugely 2026 Raipur Recommendation If rental income priority: Flat in Amanaka or VIP Road. If long-term appreciation priority: RERA-registered plot in Naya Raipur or Sejbahar corridor. Best combo: Flat for yield + Plot for growth — if budget allows split.",
