      "description": "Yeh ek question hai jise log poochh ke bhi poochh nahi lete: \"Abhi sahi time hai Raipur mein invest karne ka?\" Short answer: Haan. Long answer: Yahan hai. Why Now (2026) is the Window Infrastructure v...",
      "content_html": "<p>Yeh ek question hai jise log poochh ke bhi poochh nahi lete: \"Abhi sahi time hai Raipur mein invest karne ka?\" Short answer: Haan. Long answer: Yahan hai.</p>\n    <h3>Why Now (2026) is the Window</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Infrastructure visible but not yet fully complete — prices haven't peaked</li>\n      <li>Home loan rates near 7% — EMI affordability at multi-year best</li>\n      <li>City still in pre-institutional-discovery phase — retail investor advantage</li>\n      <li>Naya Raipur development accelerating — value catalyst upcoming</li>\n      <li>Choice still available — prime locations not sold out yet</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>What Happens If You Wait</h3>\n    <p>Real estate wisdom: The cost of waiting is usually higher than the cost of entry. In Raipur, if Naya Raipur matures over 2026-2028, early buyers capture the full appreciation. Waiters enter at higher prices with lower yield.</p>\n    <h3>What to Watch as Entry Signal</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>RERA-verified project with clear possession timeline</li>\n      <li>Developer with delivered project history in Raipur</li>\n      <li>Micro-market near announced infrastructure project</li>\n      <li>Price per sq ft still below ₹5,000 in target area</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Bottom line:</strong> Jo Raipur mein 2026 mein enter karta hai, woh 2029-2031 mein shukriyaada kar raha hoga. The window is real. Aur windows close ho jaati hain.</p>",
      "content_text": "Yeh ek question hai jise log poochh ke bhi poochh nahi lete: \"Abhi sahi time hai Raipur mein invest karne ka?\" Short answer: Haan. Long answer: Yahan hai. Why Now (2026) is the Window Infrastructure visible but not yet fully complete — prices haven't peaked Home loan rates near 7% — EMI affordability at multi-year best City still in pre-institutional-discovery phase — retail investor advantage Naya Raipur development accelerating — value catalyst upcoming Choice still available — prime locations not sold out yet What Happens If You Wait Real estate wisdom: The cost of waiting is usually higher than the cost of entry. In Raipur, if Naya Raipur matures over 2026-2028, early buyers capture the full appreciation. Waiters enter at higher prices with lower yield. What to Watch as Entry Signal RERA-verified project with clear possession timeline Developer with delivered project history in Raipur Micro-market near announced infrastructure project Price per sq ft still below ₹5,000 in target area Bottom line: Jo Raipur mein 2026 mein enter karta hai, woh 2029-2031 mein shukriyaada kar raha hoga. The window is real. Aur windows close ho jaati hain.",
