      "description": "Har investment mein risk hota hai. Jo risk ko pretend karta hai ki exist nahi karta — woh investor nahi, woh gambler hai. Raipur ke risks aur opportunities — honest assessment. Real Opportunities Indi...",
      "content_html": "<p>Har investment mein risk hota hai. Jo risk ko pretend karta hai ki exist nahi karta — woh investor nahi, woh gambler hai. Raipur ke risks aur opportunities — honest assessment.</p>\n    <h3>Real Opportunities</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>India's most affordable major Tier-2 city — lowest entry cost</li>\n      <li>Smart City + Naya Raipur = government-backed value catalyst</li>\n      <li>Rental yields among highest in Central India (7.1% max)</li>\n      <li>State capital stability — government job demand floor</li>\n      <li>Industrial ecosystem — steel, cement, power professionals migrating</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Real Risks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Infrastructure timelines can delay — Naya Raipur full development may take longer</li>\n      <li>Developer quality variance — some small builders RERA non-compliant</li>\n      <li>Liquidity risk — Raipur market thinner than metros, exit may take time</li>\n      <li>Employment concentration risk — heavy dependence on government and one or two industries</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>How to Mitigate Risks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Only RERA-registered projects (check PCGRERA portal)</li>\n      <li>Developers with delivered projects — verify possession history</li>\n      <li>5-7 year minimum hold commitment</li>\n      <li>Prefer established micro-markets for first investment</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Risk-reward balance:</strong> Raipur ka risk profile lower hai aur opportunity profile higher hai compared to overvalued metro micro-markets. Calculated risk hai, blind faith nahi.</p>",
      "content_text": "Har investment mein risk hota hai. Jo risk ko pretend karta hai ki exist nahi karta — woh investor nahi, woh gambler hai. Raipur ke risks aur opportunities — honest assessment. Real Opportunities India's most affordable major Tier-2 city — lowest entry cost Smart City + Naya Raipur = government-backed value catalyst Rental yields among highest in Central India (7.1% max) State capital stability — government job demand floor Industrial ecosystem — steel, cement, power professionals migrating Real Risks Infrastructure timelines can delay — Naya Raipur full development may take longer Developer quality variance — some small builders RERA non-compliant Liquidity risk — Raipur market thinner than metros, exit may take time Employment concentration risk — heavy dependence on government and one or two industries How to Mitigate Risks Only RERA-registered projects (check PCGRERA portal) Developers with delivered projects — verify possession history 5-7 year minimum hold commitment Prefer established micro-markets for first investment Risk-reward balance: Raipur ka risk profile lower hai aur opportunity profile higher hai compared to overvalued metro micro-markets. Calculated risk hai, blind faith nahi.",
