      "description": "Raipur mein aaj jo area \"cheap\" lag raha hai, woh kal ka \"prime\" ho sakta hai. Yeh 5 emerging areas radar par hone chahiye. 1. Boria Kalan 164.3% price appreciation already in 3 years. Infrastructure ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein aaj jo area \"cheap\" lag raha hai, woh kal ka \"prime\" ho sakta hai. Yeh 5 emerging areas radar par hone chahiye.</p>\n    <h3>1. Boria Kalan</h3>\n    <p>164.3% price appreciation already in 3 years. Infrastructure expanding. Early entrants already winning. New development pipeline strong.</p>\n    <h3>2. Abhanpur</h3>\n    <p>60% appreciation. Affordable at ₹1,200/sq ft. Highway connectivity improving. Future industrial and residential growth area.</p>\n    <h3>3. Naya Raipur Outer Sectors</h3>\n    <p>Planned development but still early in absorption. ₹700-1,500/sq ft range. Highest upside but patience required.</p>\n    <h3>4. Mandir Hasaud</h3>\n    <p>Very affordable (₹600/sq ft) — maximum affordability entry point. Long-term as city expands outward, appreciation potential significant.</p>\n    <h3>5. Kachna (Established but Growing)</h3>\n    <p>Existing residential area with quality projects launching. Villa and plot options. Emerging premium positioning. Good balance of established and growth.</p>\n    <h3>Key Principle</h3>\n    <p>Tomorrow's prime areas are today's \"too far\" areas — but only if infrastructure is coming. Always invest based on announced, funded infrastructure — not speculation. In Raipur, multiple government-backed projects are creating tomorrow's hotspots today.</p>",
      "content_text": "Raipur mein aaj jo area \"cheap\" lag raha hai, woh kal ka \"prime\" ho sakta hai. Yeh 5 emerging areas radar par hone chahiye. 1. Boria Kalan 164.3% price appreciation already in 3 years. Infrastructure expanding. Early entrants already winning. New development pipeline strong. 2. Abhanpur 60% appreciation. Affordable at ₹1,200/sq ft. Highway connectivity improving. Future industrial and residential growth area. 3. Naya Raipur Outer Sectors Planned development but still early in absorption. ₹700-1,500/sq ft range. Highest upside but patience required. 4. Mandir Hasaud Very affordable (₹600/sq ft) — maximum affordability entry point. Long-term as city expands outward, appreciation potential significant. 5. Kachna (Established but Growing) Existing residential area with quality projects launching. Villa and plot options. Emerging premium positioning. Good balance of established and growth. Key Principle Tomorrow's prime areas are today's \"too far\" areas — but only if infrastructure is coming. Always invest based on announced, funded infrastructure — not speculation. In Raipur, multiple government-backed projects are creating tomorrow's hotspots today.",
