      "description": "Raipur mein sabko crores nahi chahiye. ₹15 lakh se ₹70 lakh tak ke alag-alag budget options hain. Aapke budget ke hisaab se kya milega? ₹15-25 Lakh Budget Affordable plotted schemes in Abhanpur, Mandi...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein sabko crores nahi chahiye. ₹15 lakh se ₹70 lakh tak ke alag-alag budget options hain. Aapke budget ke hisaab se kya milega?</p>\n    <h3>₹15-25 Lakh Budget</h3>\n    <p>Affordable plotted schemes in Abhanpur, Mandir Hasaud. Small 1BHK in peripheral areas. Pure land investment in fringe zones. Best for long-term hold (7-10 yr).</p>\n    <h3>₹25-45 Lakh Budget</h3>\n    <p>Good 2BHK flat in Saddu, Sejbahar, Bhatagaon. RERA-registered society with amenities. Immediate rental possibility. Sweet spot for first-time investors in Raipur.</p>\n    <h3>₹45-70 Lakh Budget</h3>\n    <p>3BHK in established areas (Shankar Nagar, Avanti Vihar). Premium 2BHK in VIP Road. Plot in Naya Raipur developing sectors. Better quality, better rental command.</p>\n    <h3>₹70 Lakh+</h3>\n    <p>Villa projects in Kachna. Large plots in Naya Raipur. Premium gated communities. Best appreciation + lifestyle combination.</p>\n    <h3>Pro Tips for Budget Investors</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Under-construction RERA projects give 10-15% lower price vs ready</li>\n      <li>Pre-launch (from reputed builders only) can give 5-10% additional discount</li>\n      <li>Plot + construction later model gives cost control</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Key:</strong> Raipur ka beauty yahi hai — har budget mein quality product milta hai. Metro mein ₹40L mein nothing. Raipur mein ₹40L mein life.</p>",
