      "description": "Luxury sirf Mumbai aur Gurgaon mein nahi hoti. Raipur mein bhi ek growing luxury segment hai — aur yeh interesting opportunity create kar raha hai. What Counts as Luxury in Raipur ₹80 lakh to ₹2 crore...",
      "content_html": "<p>Luxury sirf Mumbai aur Gurgaon mein nahi hoti. Raipur mein bhi ek growing luxury segment hai — aur yeh interesting opportunity create kar raha hai.</p>\n    <h3>What Counts as Luxury in Raipur</h3>\n    <p>₹80 lakh to ₹2 crore range — villas, penthouses, premium gated communities. Amenities: swimming pool, clubhouse, gym, landscaped gardens, security. Locations: Vidhan Sabha Road, VIP Road, Kachna, Shankar Nagar.</p>\n    <h3>Who is Buying Luxury in Raipur</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Industrialists from steel/cement/power sector</li>\n      <li>Senior government officials</li>\n      <li>NRIs from Chhattisgarh roots</li>\n      <li>Business families upgrading lifestyle</li>\n      <li>Professionals moving from metros seeking better quality of life</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Why Luxury in Raipur is Interesting</h3>\n    <p>Mumbai mein ₹2 crore mein luxury ki koi guarantee nahi. Raipur mein ₹80L-1.5Cr mein genuinely premium product milta hai — 3,000+ sq ft, villa format, all amenities. NRI buyers especially finding this compelling.</p>\n    <h3>Investment Case</h3>\n    <p>Luxury segment mein resale typically at premium. Rental yields lower (3-4%) but absolute rental amount strong. As Raipur grows, luxury supply limited — premium narrows. Good long-term hold.</p>\n    <p><strong>For those who want luxury lifestyle without metro budget — Raipur is India's best kept secret in 2026.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Luxury sirf Mumbai aur Gurgaon mein nahi hoti. Raipur mein bhi ek growing luxury segment hai — aur yeh interesting opportunity create kar raha hai. What Counts as Luxury in Raipur ₹80 lakh to ₹2 crore range — villas, penthouses, premium gated communities. Amenities: swimming pool, clubhouse, gym, landscaped gardens, security. Locations: Vidhan Sabha Road, VIP Road, Kachna, Shankar Nagar. Who is Buying Luxury in Raipur Industrialists from steel/cement/power sector Senior government officials NRIs from Chhattisgarh roots Business families upgrading lifestyle Professionals moving from metros seeking better quality of life Why Luxury in Raipur is Interesting Mumbai mein ₹2 crore mein luxury ki koi guarantee nahi. Raipur mein ₹80L-1.5Cr mein genuinely premium product milta hai — 3,000+ sq ft, villa format, all amenities. NRI buyers especially finding this compelling. Investment Case Luxury segment mein resale typically at premium. Rental yields lower (3-4%) but absolute rental amount strong. As Raipur grows, luxury supply limited — premium narrows. Good long-term hold. For those who want luxury lifestyle without metro budget — Raipur is India's best kept secret in 2026.",
