      "description": "Raipur mein sirf residential nahi — commercial real estate bhi ek growing opportunity hai. Shops, offices, malls, warehouses — yeh sab expanding hain. Commercial Segments in Raipur Retail Shops/Showro...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein sirf residential nahi — commercial real estate bhi ek growing opportunity hai. Shops, offices, malls, warehouses — yeh sab expanding hain.</p>\n    <h3>Commercial Segments in Raipur</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Retail Shops/Showrooms:</strong> High street commercial in VIP Road, Pandri, Raipur Main Market area</li>\n      <li><strong>Office Spaces:</strong> Growing demand from government contractors, service companies, IT firms entering Chhattisgarh</li>\n      <li><strong>Mall Space:</strong> Malls expanding — retail investment in growing consumption market</li>\n      <li><strong>Warehouse/Industrial:</strong> VSIP industrial area and corridors near highways</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Commercial Yield vs Residential</h3>\n    <p>Commercial typically gives 6-9% rental yield — higher than residential. But entry cost higher, liquidity lower, tenant risk higher. Best for investors with larger capital base.</p>\n    <h3>Key Commercial Zones</h3>\n    <p>Naya Raipur commercial plots — government-planned commercial zones. As administrative center develops, demand for office space, retail, hospitality will grow. Early commercial investment in Naya Raipur = potential 3-5x in 7-10 years.</p>\n    <h3>Caution</h3>\n    <p>Commercial mein vacancy risk higher. Empty shop/office = zero income. Buy commercial only with clear demand visibility — near established footfall zones or announced institutional tenants.</p>",
