      "description": "Raipur mein land (plot) investment ek highly popular choice hai. Lekin land khareedna risky bhi ho sakta hai agar sahi process follow na ki jaaye. Complete guide. Types of Land in Raipur NA (Non-Agric...",
      "content_html": "<p>Raipur mein land (plot) investment ek highly popular choice hai. Lekin land khareedna risky bhi ho sakta hai agar sahi process follow na ki jaaye. Complete guide.</p>\n    <h3>Types of Land in Raipur</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>NA (Non-Agricultural) converted plots — build immediately</li>\n      <li>Residential layout plots — RERA registered schemes</li>\n      <li>Agricultural land — needs conversion (longer process)</li>\n      <li>Government scheme plots (Chhattisgarh Housing Board)</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Where to Buy Land in Raipur</h3>\n    <p>Naya Raipur sectors (highest potential), Kachna, Abhanpur, Old Dhamtari Road, Vidhan Sabha Road corridor — these areas have clear development vision and better title clarity.</p>\n    <h3>Due Diligence — 5 Critical Steps</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Verify RERA registration of the layout/scheme</li>\n      <li>Check land title — khatian, mutation records at tehsil</li>\n      <li>Confirm NA conversion if agricultural land</li>\n      <li>Survey/demarcation by certified surveyor</li>\n      <li>Sale agreement with registered lawyer review</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Best Entry Strategy</h3>\n    <p>RERA-registered plotted development from established builder. ₹15-50 lakh range provides good options in Raipur's growing corridors. Hold 5-7 years minimum.</p>\n    <p><strong>Rule 1:</strong> Never buy land based only on verbal promise. RERA registration = the minimum bar, always.</p>",
      "content_text": "Raipur mein land (plot) investment ek highly popular choice hai. Lekin land khareedna risky bhi ho sakta hai agar sahi process follow na ki jaaye. Complete guide. Types of Land in Raipur NA (Non-Agricultural) converted plots — build immediately Residential layout plots — RERA registered schemes Agricultural land — needs conversion (longer process) Government scheme plots (Chhattisgarh Housing Board) Where to Buy Land in Raipur Naya Raipur sectors (highest potential), Kachna, Abhanpur, Old Dhamtari Road, Vidhan Sabha Road corridor — these areas have clear development vision and better title clarity. Due Diligence — 5 Critical Steps Verify RERA registration of the layout/scheme Check land title — khatian, mutation records at tehsil Confirm NA conversion if agricultural land Survey/demarcation by certified surveyor Sale agreement with registered lawyer review Best Entry Strategy RERA-registered plotted development from established builder. ₹15-50 lakh range provides good options in Raipur's growing corridors. Hold 5-7 years minimum. Rule 1: Never buy land based only on verbal promise. RERA registration = the minimum bar, always.",
