      "description": "Real estate mein ek rule hai: \"Location, location, location.\" Lekin uss location ko define karta hai infrastructure. Raipur mein kaun sa infrastructure property prices badha raha hai? Road Infrastruct...",
      "content_html": "<p>Real estate mein ek rule hai: \"Location, location, location.\" Lekin uss location ko define karta hai infrastructure. Raipur mein kaun sa infrastructure property prices badha raha hai?</p>\n    <h3>Road Infrastructure</h3>\n    <p>Raipur ring road, flyovers, highway expansion — yeh directly surrounding land value badhate hain. Areas jo pehle \"too far\" the, ab 20 min mein accessible hain. Abhanpur and Mandir Hasaud — ring road beneficiaries.</p>\n    <h3>Naya Raipur Development</h3>\n    <p>Planned city with 90m wide roads, dedicated commercial and residential zones, government offices. As institutions shift — demand for housing in that corridor explodes. Early buyers already seeing appreciation.</p>\n    <h3>Airport Connectivity</h3>\n    <p>Swami Vivekananda Airport expansion — more routes, more business travelers, more real estate demand. Premium housing near airport corridors sees uplift.</p>\n    <h3>Educational Institutions</h3>\n    <p>IIT Bhilai (near Raipur), AIIMS Raipur, NIT Raipur — institutional catchment creates sustained demand for student and faculty housing. Near-campus areas see strong rental demand.</p>\n    <h3>Future Infrastructure Pending</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Metro rail connectivity discussion ongoing</li>\n      <li>BRTS expansion</li>\n      <li>IT park in Naya Raipur — would be transformational</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Rule:</strong> Invest near announced, funded infrastructure — not speculative infrastructure. In Raipur, multiple confirmed projects create clear value catalysts.</p>",
      "content_text": "Real estate mein ek rule hai: \"Location, location, location.\" Lekin uss location ko define karta hai infrastructure. Raipur mein kaun sa infrastructure property prices badha raha hai? Road Infrastructure Raipur ring road, flyovers, highway expansion — yeh directly surrounding land value badhate hain. Areas jo pehle \"too far\" the, ab 20 min mein accessible hain. Abhanpur and Mandir Hasaud — ring road beneficiaries. Naya Raipur Development Planned city with 90m wide roads, dedicated commercial and residential zones, government offices. As institutions shift — demand for housing in that corridor explodes. Early buyers already seeing appreciation. Airport Connectivity Swami Vivekananda Airport expansion — more routes, more business travelers, more real estate demand. Premium housing near airport corridors sees uplift. Educational Institutions IIT Bhilai (near Raipur), AIIMS Raipur, NIT Raipur — institutional catchment creates sustained demand for student and faculty housing. Near-campus areas see strong rental demand. Future Infrastructure Pending Metro rail connectivity discussion ongoing BRTS expansion IT park in Naya Raipur — would be transformational Rule: Invest near announced, funded infrastructure — not speculative infrastructure. In Raipur, multiple confirmed projects create clear value catalysts.",
