      "description": "₹25 lakh — yeh amount metros mein kuch khaas nahi karta. Lekin sahi city mein yeh ek genuine property investment ki shuruat ho sakti hai. Option A: Raipur — 2BHK Flat Entry ₹25L down payment on a ₹35-...",
      "content_html": "<p>₹25 lakh — yeh amount metros mein kuch khaas nahi karta. Lekin sahi city mein yeh ek genuine property investment ki shuruat ho sakti hai.</p>\n    <h3>Option A: Raipur — 2BHK Flat Entry</h3>\n    <p>₹25L down payment on a ₹35-40L 2BHK in Saddu or Sejbahar. Balance ₹10-15L on home loan. EMI ~₹10,000-12,000. Rental possibility: ₹10,000-14,000. Near breakeven from day one.</p>\n    <h3>Option B: Plot in Emerging Micro-Market</h3>\n    <p>Full ₹25L in a RERA-registered plotted scheme in Raipur's Abhanpur or Boria Kalan corridor. No EMI. Pure appreciation play. 5-7 year hold for 2-3x target.</p>\n    <h3>Option C: Nagpur Under-Construction</h3>\n    <p>₹25L down payment on ₹45-50L apartment near MIHAN. Builder payment plan spreads balance. Possession in 2-3 years. Appreciation during construction period.</p>\n    <h3>Option D: Fractional Commercial</h3>\n    <p>Invest ₹25L in SM-REIT or fractional platform in Grade-A commercial. 8-10% annual return projected. Higher liquidity than direct property. Good for diversification.</p>\n    <h3>Best Choice?</h3>\n    <p>For most investors at ₹25L: <strong>Option A or B in Raipur.</strong> Option A gives yield + appreciation. Option B gives pure appreciation play. Both are strong 2026 picks in an affordable, early-stage market.</p>",
      "content_text": "₹25 lakh — yeh amount metros mein kuch khaas nahi karta. Lekin sahi city mein yeh ek genuine property investment ki shuruat ho sakti hai. Option A: Raipur — 2BHK Flat Entry ₹25L down payment on a ₹35-40L 2BHK in Saddu or Sejbahar. Balance ₹10-15L on home loan. EMI ~₹10,000-12,000. Rental possibility: ₹10,000-14,000. Near breakeven from day one. Option B: Plot in Emerging Micro-Market Full ₹25L in a RERA-registered plotted scheme in Raipur's Abhanpur or Boria Kalan corridor. No EMI. Pure appreciation play. 5-7 year hold for 2-3x target. Option C: Nagpur Under-Construction ₹25L down payment on ₹45-50L apartment near MIHAN. Builder payment plan spreads balance. Possession in 2-3 years. Appreciation during construction period. Option D: Fractional Commercial Invest ₹25L in SM-REIT or fractional platform in Grade-A commercial. 8-10% annual return projected. Higher liquidity than direct property. Good for diversification. Best Choice? For most investors at ₹25L: Option A or B in Raipur. Option A gives yield + appreciation. Option B gives pure appreciation play. Both are strong 2026 picks in an affordable, early-stage market.",
