      "description": "City toh pata hai — Raipur, Nagpur, ya Indore. Lekin city ke andar exactly kahan invest karein? Yeh micro-market selection ka science hai. 6 Signals of a High-ROI Micro-Market Signal 1 — New Road/Flyo...",
      "content_html": "<p>City toh pata hai — Raipur, Nagpur, ya Indore. Lekin city ke andar exactly kahan invest karein? Yeh micro-market selection ka science hai.</p>\n    <h3>6 Signals of a High-ROI Micro-Market</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Signal 1 — New Road/Flyover Announced:</strong> Connectivity improvement = price jump incoming. Buy before road complete.</li>\n      <li><strong>Signal 2 — Institutional Development Nearby:</strong> Hospital, college, IT park, government office = sustained demand anchor</li>\n      <li><strong>Signal 3 — Rental Demand Higher than Supply:</strong> Vacancy rate low = strong yield = healthy market</li>\n      <li><strong>Signal 4 — Developer Activity Increasing:</strong> Multiple developers launching = confident in area's future</li>\n      <li><strong>Signal 5 — Migration Pattern:</strong> People moving into area from other parts of city = emerging desirability</li>\n      <li><strong>Signal 6 — Price Gap vs Adjacent Established Areas:</strong> Large discount to established nearby area = catch-up potential</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Raipur Application</h3>\n    <p>Boria Kalan had all 6 signals 3 years ago — result: 164% appreciation. Naya Raipur outer sectors show signals 1, 2, 4 today. Early buyers will capture the next wave.</p>\n    <h3>Research Method</h3>\n    <p>Talk to 5 local brokers. Visit in person. Check 99acres/MagicBricks for price trends. Read local news for infrastructure announcements. Walk the area — feel the momentum.</p>\n    <p><strong>The best micro-market research tool is your feet — go visit, talk to people, feel the energy. Data confirms what instinct finds.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "City toh pata hai — Raipur, Nagpur, ya Indore. Lekin city ke andar exactly kahan invest karein? Yeh micro-market selection ka science hai. 6 Signals of a High-ROI Micro-Market Signal 1 — New Road/Flyover Announced: Connectivity improvement = price jump incoming. Buy before road complete. Signal 2 — Institutional Development Nearby: Hospital, college, IT park, government office = sustained demand anchor Signal 3 — Rental Demand Higher than Supply: Vacancy rate low = strong yield = healthy market Signal 4 — Developer Activity Increasing: Multiple developers launching = confident in area's future Signal 5 — Migration Pattern: People moving into area from other parts of city = emerging desirability Signal 6 — Price Gap vs Adjacent Established Areas: Large discount to established nearby area = catch-up potential Raipur Application Boria Kalan had all 6 signals 3 years ago — result: 164% appreciation. Naya Raipur outer sectors show signals 1, 2, 4 today. Early buyers will capture the next wave. Research Method Talk to 5 local brokers. Visit in person. Check 99acres/MagicBricks for price trends. Read local news for infrastructure announcements. Walk the area — feel the momentum. The best micro-market research tool is your feet — go visit, talk to people, feel the energy. Data confirms what instinct finds.",
