      "description": "Koi bhi property finalize karne se pehle yeh 15-point checklist complete karo. Ek bhi point miss hua toh regret possible hai. Legal Checks ☐ RERA registration verified on state portal ☐ Title search d...",
      "content_html": "<p>Koi bhi property finalize karne se pehle yeh 15-point checklist complete karo. Ek bhi point miss hua toh regret possible hai.</p>\n    <h3>Legal Checks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>☐ RERA registration verified on state portal</li>\n      <li>☐ Title search done by independent lawyer</li>\n      <li>☐ No encumbrance on property</li>\n      <li>☐ Building approval from local authority</li>\n      <li>☐ NA conversion if agricultural land</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Financial Checks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>☐ Total cost calculated (price + stamp duty + registration + brokerage + interior)</li>\n      <li>☐ EMI within 40% of monthly income</li>\n      <li>☐ Emergency fund intact post down payment</li>\n      <li>☐ Rental yield verified with local broker (not developer)</li>\n      <li>☐ Compared minimum 3 similar properties</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Developer Checks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>☐ Developer has delivered 2+ projects in same city</li>\n      <li>☐ Site visit done — check construction quality</li>\n      <li>☐ Existing residents/buyers talked to</li>\n      <li>☐ Escrow account confirmed for payments</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Market Checks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>☐ Area growth drivers identified (infrastructure, employment)</li>\n      <li>☐ Exit buyer market exists — who will buy from you?</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>All 15 ticks? Ab sign karo. Miss even 3? Pause aur reconsider.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Koi bhi property finalize karne se pehle yeh 15-point checklist complete karo. Ek bhi point miss hua toh regret possible hai. Legal Checks ☐ RERA registration verified on state portal ☐ Title search done by independent lawyer ☐ No encumbrance on property ☐ Building approval from local authority ☐ NA conversion if agricultural land Financial Checks ☐ Total cost calculated (price + stamp duty + registration + brokerage + interior) ☐ EMI within 40% of monthly income ☐ Emergency fund intact post down payment ☐ Rental yield verified with local broker (not developer) ☐ Compared minimum 3 similar properties Developer Checks ☐ Developer has delivered 2+ projects in same city ☐ Site visit done — check construction quality ☐ Existing residents/buyers talked to ☐ Escrow account confirmed for payments Market Checks ☐ Area growth drivers identified (infrastructure, employment) ☐ Exit buyer market exists — who will buy from you? All 15 ticks? Ab sign karo. Miss even 3? Pause aur reconsider.",
