      "description": "Crores of Indians abroad. Lakho unke paas investable dollars hain. India real estate unke liye ek natural home — financially aur emotionally. Complete NRI guide. NRI Kya Khareed Sakta Hai Residential ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Crores of Indians abroad. Lakho unke paas investable dollars hain. India real estate unke liye ek natural home — financially aur emotionally. Complete NRI guide.</p>\n    <h3>NRI Kya Khareed Sakta Hai</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Residential and commercial property — yes, freely</li>\n      <li>Agricultural land, plantation property, farmhouse — no (without RBI permission)</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Repatriation Rules</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Property khareedne ke liye NRE/NRO account se payment</li>\n      <li>Rental income NRO account mein</li>\n      <li>Sale proceeds repatriation: $1M per year allowed</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Tax Implications</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>TDS on rental income: 30% (higher than resident Indian 30% slab)</li>\n      <li>Capital gains tax similar to residents with DTAA benefits</li>\n      <li>Consult CA for specific country treaty benefits</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Why India Real Estate Makes Sense for NRIs</h3>\n    <p>Dollar/Euro/Pound vs Rupee advantage — appreciation in foreign currency terms is additional. India urbanisation long-term thesis intact. Emotional connection to ancestral city (Raipur for Chhattisgarh NRIs). Managing property remotely now easier via property managers.</p>\n    <h3>Best Cities for NRI Investment 2026</h3>\n    <p>Tier-2 cities with family roots. Raipur for Chhattisgarh NRIs — genuine affordability + growth story. Hire local RERA-verified broker for property management.</p>",
      "content_text": "Crores of Indians abroad. Lakho unke paas investable dollars hain. India real estate unke liye ek natural home — financially aur emotionally. Complete NRI guide. NRI Kya Khareed Sakta Hai Residential and commercial property — yes, freely Agricultural land, plantation property, farmhouse — no (without RBI permission) Repatriation Rules Property khareedne ke liye NRE/NRO account se payment Rental income NRO account mein Sale proceeds repatriation: $1M per year allowed Tax Implications TDS on rental income: 30% (higher than resident Indian 30% slab) Capital gains tax similar to residents with DTAA benefits Consult CA for specific country treaty benefits Why India Real Estate Makes Sense for NRIs Dollar/Euro/Pound vs Rupee advantage — appreciation in foreign currency terms is additional. India urbanisation long-term thesis intact. Emotional connection to ancestral city (Raipur for Chhattisgarh NRIs). Managing property remotely now easier via property managers. Best Cities for NRI Investment 2026 Tier-2 cities with family roots. Raipur for Chhattisgarh NRIs — genuine affordability + growth story. Hire local RERA-verified broker for property management.",
