      "description": "Objection aane par weak broker defensive ho jaata hai. Strong broker curious ho jaata hai — \"kyun soch rahe hain yeh?\" Handle objections like a pro. Top 5 Real Estate Objections + Responses \"Price bah...",
      "content_html": "<p>Objection aane par weak broker defensive ho jaata hai. Strong broker curious ho jaata hai — \"kyun soch rahe hain yeh?\" Handle objections like a pro.</p>\n    <h3>Top 5 Real Estate Objections + Responses</h3>\n    <h3>\"Price bahut zyada hai\"</h3>\n    <p>Response: \"Main samajh sakta hoon. Aapka target range kya tha? [Listen.] Chaliye dekhte hain us budget mein kya best milta hai — aur comparison karte hain is property ki value ke saath.\"</p>\n    <h3>\"Pehle thoda wait karte hain\"</h3>\n    <p>Response: \"Bilkul. Main jab aapko data bhejta hoon — is area mein last 12 mahine mein price trend, aur EMI at current rates — toh wait karne ka real cost clear ho jaayega.\"</p>\n    <h3>\"Builder par trust nahi hai\"</h3>\n    <p>Response: \"Fair concern. Main aapko unke 3 delivered projects ke registered buyers se connect kar sakta hoon. Unka feedback first-hand hoga.\"</p>\n    <h3>\"Ghar mein discussion karna hai\"</h3>\n    <p>Response: \"Zaroor. Main ek small presentation send karta hoon jo unhe bhi picture clear kare. Aur agar unke koi specific sawaal hon, main directly unse bhi baat kar sakta hoon.\"</p>\n    <h3>\"Location acchi nahi hai\"</h3>\n    <p>Response: \"Kaunsa specific concern hai — connectivity, schools, commercial? Let me show you what's coming in the next 2 years around this area.\"</p>\n    <p><strong>Objection handling rule: Never argue. Always acknowledge, then redirect. \"I understand. Here's the data that might change the picture.\"</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Objection aane par weak broker defensive ho jaata hai. Strong broker curious ho jaata hai — \"kyun soch rahe hain yeh?\" Handle objections like a pro. Top 5 Real Estate Objections + Responses \"Price bahut zyada hai\" Response: \"Main samajh sakta hoon. Aapka target range kya tha? [Listen.] Chaliye dekhte hain us budget mein kya best milta hai — aur comparison karte hain is property ki value ke saath.\" \"Pehle thoda wait karte hain\" Response: \"Bilkul. Main jab aapko data bhejta hoon — is area mein last 12 mahine mein price trend, aur EMI at current rates — toh wait karne ka real cost clear ho jaayega.\" \"Builder par trust nahi hai\" Response: \"Fair concern. Main aapko unke 3 delivered projects ke registered buyers se connect kar sakta hoon. Unka feedback first-hand hoga.\" \"Ghar mein discussion karna hai\" Response: \"Zaroor. Main ek small presentation send karta hoon jo unhe bhi picture clear kare. Aur agar unke koi specific sawaal hon, main directly unse bhi baat kar sakta hoon.\" \"Location acchi nahi hai\" Response: \"Kaunsa specific concern hai — connectivity, schools, commercial? Let me show you what's coming in the next 2 years around this area.\" Objection handling rule: Never argue. Always acknowledge, then redirect. \"I understand. Here's the data that might change the picture.\"",
