      "description": "Real estate broker ke liye social media sirf posting nahi — lead machine hai. Lekin sahi content + sahi platform + sahi targeting chahiye. Blueprint yeh hai. Platform Strategy Facebook: 35+ age group....",
      "content_html": "<p>Real estate broker ke liye social media sirf posting nahi — lead machine hai. Lekin sahi content + sahi platform + sahi targeting chahiye. Blueprint yeh hai.</p>\n    <h3>Platform Strategy</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Facebook:</strong> 35+ age group. Most real estate buyers ka age band. Local area groups mein active raho. FB Ads for targeted leads.</li>\n      <li><strong>Instagram:</strong> 25-40 age group. Reels for visibility. Stories for engagement. Property tour videos.</li>\n      <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> Long-form content. \"Raipur mein property kahan aur kyun\" — search se leads aate hain. Slow build but highest quality leads.</li>\n      <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> HNI and corporate buyers. Market analysis content. Best for high-ticket leads.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Content Mix (80-20 Rule)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>80% — Valuable content: market insights, area tours, buyer education, FAQs</li>\n      <li>20% — Promotional: property listings, project launches, testimonials</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Lead Capture</h3>\n    <p>Content gets attention. Lead magnet captures them. Examples: \"Free Raipur Investment Guide 2026\" — download form. \"Property ROI Calculator\" — tool that requires email/number. \"Free consultation call\" — direct booking.</p>\n    <h3>Consistency > Virality</h3>\n    <p>One viral post dekh lete hain. 200 posts ka author — usse trust karte hain. Post consistently, not brilliantly. 3 posts/week, 52 weeks = 156 posts = deep expertise signal to audience.</p>",
      "content_text": "Real estate broker ke liye social media sirf posting nahi — lead machine hai. Lekin sahi content + sahi platform + sahi targeting chahiye. Blueprint yeh hai. Platform Strategy Facebook: 35+ age group. Most real estate buyers ka age band. Local area groups mein active raho. FB Ads for targeted leads. Instagram: 25-40 age group. Reels for visibility. Stories for engagement. Property tour videos. YouTube: Long-form content. \"Raipur mein property kahan aur kyun\" — search se leads aate hain. Slow build but highest quality leads. LinkedIn: HNI and corporate buyers. Market analysis content. Best for high-ticket leads. Content Mix (80-20 Rule) 80% — Valuable content: market insights, area tours, buyer education, FAQs 20% — Promotional: property listings, project launches, testimonials Lead Capture Content gets attention. Lead magnet captures them. Examples: \"Free Raipur Investment Guide 2026\" — download form. \"Property ROI Calculator\" — tool that requires email/number. \"Free consultation call\" — direct booking. Consistency > Virality One viral post dekh lete hain. 200 posts ka author — usse trust karte hain. Post consistently, not brilliantly. 3 posts/week, 52 weeks = 156 posts = deep expertise signal to audience.",
