      "description": "Broker sabse zyada kiski baat karta hai? Leads. Lekin real wealth commission optimization se banti hai. Same deals, higher income — yeh possible hai. Strategy 1: High-Value Property Focus ₹50L propert...",
      "content_html": "<p>Broker sabse zyada kiski baat karta hai? Leads. Lekin real wealth commission optimization se banti hai. Same deals, higher income — yeh possible hai.</p>\n    <h3>Strategy 1: High-Value Property Focus</h3>\n    <p>₹50L property bechna aur ₹1.5 Cr property bechna — effort roughly similar. Commission 3x. Shift focus upward — even 2-3 high-ticket deals/month = strong income.</p>\n    <h3>Strategy 2: Dual Commission Model</h3>\n    <p>Some deals — aap seller aur buyer dono represent karo (where ethically possible and disclosed). Double commission on same deal.</p>\n    <h3>Strategy 3: Developer Referral Programs</h3>\n    <p>Beyond standard commission — some developers offer: Performance bonus (above x units/month), project exclusivity for top performers, loyalty incentives. Negotiate with key developers.</p>\n    <h3>Strategy 4: Recurring Revenue</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Property management fee: 8-10% of monthly rent from your sold properties</li>\n      <li>Rental deals: Commission on every new tenant placed</li>\n      <li>Resale listings: Your sold clients become your resale clients 5 years later</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Strategy 5: Network Override</h3>\n    <p>Build team of 5-10 sub-brokers. 20-30% override on their deals. 10 agents × ₹1L commission each × 20% override = ₹2L/month additional without you doing those deals.</p>\n    <p><strong>Commission maximize = work smarter not just harder. Higher ticket + recurring revenue + team override = broker's path to real wealth.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Broker sabse zyada kiski baat karta hai? Leads. Lekin real wealth commission optimization se banti hai. Same deals, higher income — yeh possible hai. Strategy 1: High-Value Property Focus ₹50L property bechna aur ₹1.5 Cr property bechna — effort roughly similar. Commission 3x. Shift focus upward — even 2-3 high-ticket deals/month = strong income. Strategy 2: Dual Commission Model Some deals — aap seller aur buyer dono represent karo (where ethically possible and disclosed). Double commission on same deal. Strategy 3: Developer Referral Programs Beyond standard commission — some developers offer: Performance bonus (above x units/month), project exclusivity for top performers, loyalty incentives. Negotiate with key developers. Strategy 4: Recurring Revenue Property management fee: 8-10% of monthly rent from your sold properties Rental deals: Commission on every new tenant placed Resale listings: Your sold clients become your resale clients 5 years later Strategy 5: Network Override Build team of 5-10 sub-brokers. 20-30% override on their deals. 10 agents × ₹1L commission each × 20% override = ₹2L/month additional without you doing those deals. Commission maximize = work smarter not just harder. Higher ticket + recurring revenue + team override = broker's path to real wealth.",
