      "title": "Repeat Clients Kaise Banaye",
      "slug": "repeat-clients-kaise-banaye",
      "category": "Broker & Channel Partner",
      "tags": [
        "Repeat Clients",
        "Referral Strategy"
      ],
      "description": "Naya client dhundna 5x costly hai existing client ko retain karne se — yeh sab jagah sach hai, real estate mein bhi. Repeat clients aur referrals — yeh sabse profitable segment hai. The Post-Sale Rela...",
      "content_html": "<p>Naya client dhundna 5x costly hai existing client ko retain karne se — yeh sab jagah sach hai, real estate mein bhi. Repeat clients aur referrals — yeh sabse profitable segment hai.</p>\n    <h3>The Post-Sale Relationship Blueprint</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Week 1 post-deal:</strong> Thank you call + ensure paperwork process smooth hai</li>\n      <li><strong>Month 1:</strong> Check-in — koi issue? Builder ko kuch chahiye?</li>\n      <li><strong>Month 3:</strong> Market update — \"is area mein prices aur badhi hain. Aapka investment accha ja raha hai.\"</li>\n      <li><strong>Month 6:</strong> Festival greeting + subtle referral ask: \"Koi friend/family soch raha hai?\"</li>\n      <li><strong>Annual:</strong> Property anniversary message. \"1 saal ho gaya — approximate value update.\"</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Why This Works</h3>\n    <p>Client purchase ke baad bhi aapko yaad karta hai. Jab bhi property topic aata hai circle mein — woh aapka naam leta hai. That referral = zero cost, highest conversion rate.</p>\n    <h3>Loyalty Program for Clients</h3>\n    <p>Next property purchase — reduced brokerage or additional service. Investment tracking service — quarterly portfolio value update. These small gestures build lifetime loyalty.</p>\n    <h3>The Numbers</h3>\n    <p>1 happy client × 5 referrals in lifetime × 50% conversion = 2.5 additional deals. Each referral costs zero acquisition. Same commission. Zero marketing cost. That's the real estate broker's compounding formula.</p>",
      "content_text": "Naya client dhundna 5x costly hai existing client ko retain karne se — yeh sab jagah sach hai, real estate mein bhi. Repeat clients aur referrals — yeh sabse profitable segment hai. The Post-Sale Relationship Blueprint Week 1 post-deal: Thank you call + ensure paperwork process smooth hai Month 1: Check-in — koi issue? Builder ko kuch chahiye? Month 3: Market update — \"is area mein prices aur badhi hain. Aapka investment accha ja raha hai.\" Month 6: Festival greeting + subtle referral ask: \"Koi friend/family soch raha hai?\" Annual: Property anniversary message. \"1 saal ho gaya — approximate value update.\" Why This Works Client purchase ke baad bhi aapko yaad karta hai. Jab bhi property topic aata hai circle mein — woh aapka naam leta hai. That referral = zero cost, highest conversion rate. Loyalty Program for Clients Next property purchase — reduced brokerage or additional service. Investment tracking service — quarterly portfolio value update. These small gestures build lifetime loyalty. The Numbers 1 happy client × 5 referrals in lifetime × 50% conversion = 2.5 additional deals. Each referral costs zero acquisition. Same commission. Zero marketing cost. That's the real estate broker's compounding formula.",
