      "title": "Price Trends ka Analysis Kaise Kare",
      "slug": "price-trends-ka-analysis-kaise-kare",
      "category": "Data & Micro-Market Analysis",
      "tags": [
        "Price Analysis",
        "Trend Reading"
      ],
      "description": "Price trend analysis — yeh beginner investors underestimate karte hain. Sirf \"kya hua\" nahi — \"kyon hua aur aage kya hoga\" — yahi real analysis hai. Step 1: Gather Historical Data 99acres ya MagicBric...",
      "content_html": "<p>Price trend analysis — yeh beginner investors underestimate karte hain. Sirf \"kya hua\" nahi — \"kyon hua aur aage kya hoga\" — yahi real analysis hai.</p>\n    <h3>Step 1: Gather Historical Data</h3>\n    <p>99acres ya MagicBricks par area/locality select karo. Price history 3-5 years dekho. Note: Annual price change percentage. Any unusual spikes/drops — find the cause.</p>\n    <h3>Step 2: Contextualize the Data</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Kab infrastructure project announce hua? Price jump uske aas paas tha?</li>\n      <li>COVID ke dौran kya hua? Post-COVID recovery kitni fast?</li>\n      <li>Builders ka launch timing vs price change?</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Step 3: Compare to Benchmarks</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>City average vs micro-market — outperforming ya underperforming?</li>\n      <li>National inflation vs real estate appreciation — real return kya hai?</li>\n      <li>Competing investment (Sensex, FD) vs property appreciation</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Step 4: Forward Looking</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Kya woh infrastructure jo price badhaya — abhi bhi value add kar sakta hai?</li>\n      <li>Supply pipeline kitna hai — potential oversupply risk?</li>\n      <li>Demand drivers — sustainable hain ya temporary?</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Red Flags in Price Trends</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Sudden 30%+ jump without clear infrastructure reason — speculative, unsustainable</li>\n      <li>5+ years of zero appreciation — area stagnant, structural issues</li>\n      <li>Price drop for 2+ consecutive years — demand problem</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Price trends tell the story of an area's past. Contextualizing them tells the story of its future. Both matter equally.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Price trend analysis — yeh beginner investors underestimate karte hain. Sirf \"kya hua\" nahi — \"kyon hua aur aage kya hoga\" — yahi real analysis hai. Step 1: Gather Historical Data 99acres ya MagicBricks par area/locality select karo. Price history 3-5 years dekho. Note: Annual price change percentage. Any unusual spikes/drops — find the cause. Step 2: Contextualize the Data Kab infrastructure project announce hua? Price jump uske aas paas tha? COVID ke dौran kya hua? Post-COVID recovery kitni fast? Builders ka launch timing vs price change? Step 3: Compare to Benchmarks City average vs micro-market — outperforming ya underperforming? National inflation vs real estate appreciation — real return kya hai? Competing investment (Sensex, FD) vs property appreciation Step 4: Forward Looking Kya woh infrastructure jo price badhaya — abhi bhi value add kar sakta hai? Supply pipeline kitna hai — potential oversupply risk? Demand drivers — sustainable hain ya temporary? Red Flags in Price Trends Sudden 30%+ jump without clear infrastructure reason — speculative, unsustainable 5+ years of zero appreciation — area stagnant, structural issues Price drop for 2+ consecutive years — demand problem Price trends tell the story of an area's past. Contextualizing them tells the story of its future. Both matter equally.",
