      "description": "Sahi data chahiye toh sahi source chahiye. India ke real estate ke liye best data tools aur sources — free aur paid dono. Free Sources 99acres.com: Price trends by locality, listing inventory, demand ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Sahi data chahiye toh sahi source chahiye. India ke real estate ke liye best data tools aur sources — free aur paid dono.</p>\n    <h3>Free Sources</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>99acres.com:</strong> Price trends by locality, listing inventory, demand heatmaps. Filter by BHK type and price range for micro-market data.</li>\n      <li><strong>MagicBricks.com:</strong> Price trends, area overview, new project data</li>\n      <li><strong>NoBroker:</strong> Rental data — actual rent ranges by area</li>\n      <li><strong>RBI RESIDEX:</strong> Official House Price Index — rbi.org.in</li>\n      <li><strong>RERA Portal:</strong> State-wise project registration, delivery status, developer compliance</li>\n      <li><strong>Anarock Reports:</strong> Quarterly market reports — free PDF download</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Paid Sources (Professional)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>PropEquity:</strong> Transaction data, project-level analytics, developer history</li>\n      <li><strong>JLL / Cushman Reports:</strong> Institutional-grade market reports</li>\n      <li><strong>Square Yards Data:</strong> City-level investment intelligence</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Offline Sources (Often Overlooked)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Tehsil/Sub-registrar records: Actual transaction prices (not listing) — ground truth</li>\n      <li>Local newspaper real estate supplements: Developer activity, new launch announcements</li>\n      <li>Municipal corporation website: Development plans, zone classifications, future road projects</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>Start with free tools — 99acres trends + RERA check + RBI RESIDEX. These 3 alone give you 80% of the data needed for a solid investment decision.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Sahi data chahiye toh sahi source chahiye. India ke real estate ke liye best data tools aur sources — free aur paid dono. Free Sources 99acres.com: Price trends by locality, listing inventory, demand heatmaps. Filter by BHK type and price range for micro-market data. MagicBricks.com: Price trends, area overview, new project data NoBroker: Rental data — actual rent ranges by area RBI RESIDEX: Official House Price Index — rbi.org.in RERA Portal: State-wise project registration, delivery status, developer compliance Anarock Reports: Quarterly market reports — free PDF download Paid Sources (Professional) PropEquity: Transaction data, project-level analytics, developer history JLL / Cushman Reports: Institutional-grade market reports Square Yards Data: City-level investment intelligence Offline Sources (Often Overlooked) Tehsil/Sub-registrar records: Actual transaction prices (not listing) — ground truth Local newspaper real estate supplements: Developer activity, new launch announcements Municipal corporation website: Development plans, zone classifications, future road projects Start with free tools — 99acres trends + RERA check + RBI RESIDEX. These 3 alone give you 80% of the data needed for a solid investment decision.",
