      "description": "₹50,000 in digital marketing consistently = ₹2-5 lakh commission. ROI is real. Lekin sirf paise daalne se nahi hota — sahi strategy chahiye. Complete breakdown. The Digital Marketing Stack for Real Es...",
      "content_html": "<p>₹50,000 in digital marketing consistently = ₹2-5 lakh commission. ROI is real. Lekin sirf paise daalne se nahi hota — sahi strategy chahiye. Complete breakdown.</p>\n    <h3>The Digital Marketing Stack for Real Estate</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Google Search Ads:</strong> \"Property in Raipur\" jab log search karein — aap sabse pehle milein. Intent-based — highest conversion leads.</li>\n      <li><strong>Facebook/Instagram Ads:</strong> Awareness + leads. Interest targeting: real estate, home buying, investment. Best for cold audience warming.</li>\n      <li><strong>Property Portals (99acres, MagicBricks):</strong> Aapki listings premium visibility. Featured listings = more inquiries. Cost: ₹5,000-20,000/month.</li>\n      <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> Long-term organic. Area tours, investment guides. Low cost, high trust-building.</li>\n      <li><strong>SEO (Website):</strong> \"Best property in Raipur\" blog ranking. Slow build — 6-12 months. Highest quality leads when established.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Budget Allocation (₹20,000/month)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Google Ads: ₹8,000 (40%)</li>\n      <li>Facebook/Instagram Ads: ₹7,000 (35%)</li>\n      <li>Portal listings: ₹5,000 (25%)</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Tracking What Works</h3>\n    <p>UTM links, lead source tracking, cost per lead, cost per deal — measure everything. Most brokers run ads but don't measure ROI. Those who do — optimize and win.</p>\n    <p><strong>Start small (₹5,000-10,000/month), learn what converts, then scale. Never \"set and forget\" — real estate ads need weekly optimization.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "₹50,000 in digital marketing consistently = ₹2-5 lakh commission. ROI is real. Lekin sirf paise daalne se nahi hota — sahi strategy chahiye. Complete breakdown. The Digital Marketing Stack for Real Estate Google Search Ads: \"Property in Raipur\" jab log search karein — aap sabse pehle milein. Intent-based — highest conversion leads. Facebook/Instagram Ads: Awareness + leads. Interest targeting: real estate, home buying, investment. Best for cold audience warming. Property Portals (99acres, MagicBricks): Aapki listings premium visibility. Featured listings = more inquiries. Cost: ₹5,000-20,000/month. YouTube: Long-term organic. Area tours, investment guides. Low cost, high trust-building. SEO (Website): \"Best property in Raipur\" blog ranking. Slow build — 6-12 months. Highest quality leads when established. Budget Allocation (₹20,000/month) Google Ads: ₹8,000 (40%) Facebook/Instagram Ads: ₹7,000 (35%) Portal listings: ₹5,000 (25%) Tracking What Works UTM links, lead source tracking, cost per lead, cost per deal — measure everything. Most brokers run ads but don't measure ROI. Those who do — optimize and win. Start small (₹5,000-10,000/month), learn what converts, then scale. Never \"set and forget\" — real estate ads need weekly optimization.",
