      "description": "Instagram Reels = free reach + viral potential. Property broker jo Reels nahi bana raha — woh sabse zyada bढ़te hue free marketing channel ko ignore kar raha hai. What Types of Reels Work for Real Est...",
      "content_html": "<p>Instagram Reels = free reach + viral potential. Property broker jo Reels nahi bana raha — woh sabse zyada bढ़te hue free marketing channel ko ignore kar raha hai.</p>\n    <h3>What Types of Reels Work for Real Estate</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Property Tour Reels:</strong> 30-60 second walkthrough with trending audio. Show the best features — view, kitchen, amenities. Quick cuts, good lighting.</li>\n      <li><strong>Before/After Area Reels:</strong> \"Yeh area 2019 mein kaisa tha vs 2024 mein\" — map/photo comparison. High share value.</li>\n      <li><strong>Myth-Busting Reels:</strong> \"Real estate mein ₹50L chahiye — MYTH.\" Hook + education. Expert positioning.</li>\n      <li><strong>Market Data Reels:</strong> \"Raipur mein yeh area mein 164% appreciation aayi\" — data visualized simply. High authority signal.</li>\n      <li><strong>Client Story Reels:</strong> 60 second client journey — \"3 saal pehle invest kiya, aaj ka update.\" Powerful social proof.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Reel Formula</h3>\n    <p><strong>Hook (0-3 sec):</strong> Bold text or shocking stat. <strong>Content (3-25 sec):</strong> Value delivery — tour, data, story. <strong>CTA (25-30 sec):</strong> \"Profile mein link hai ya DM karo 'Raipur' likh ke.\" Clear next step.</p>\n    <h3>Consistency is the Algorithm's Best Friend</h3>\n    <p>3 Reels/week for 3 months = 36 Reels. Algorithm rewards consistency with organic reach. By month 3, organic views compound. One of those Reels goes viral — it's done.</p>\n    <p><strong>Equipment needed: ₹0 extra. Your phone is enough. Start filming today — imperfect content beats no content every single time.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Instagram Reels = free reach + viral potential. Property broker jo Reels nahi bana raha — woh sabse zyada bढ़te hue free marketing channel ko ignore kar raha hai. What Types of Reels Work for Real Estate Property Tour Reels: 30-60 second walkthrough with trending audio. Show the best features — view, kitchen, amenities. Quick cuts, good lighting. Before/After Area Reels: \"Yeh area 2019 mein kaisa tha vs 2024 mein\" — map/photo comparison. High share value. Myth-Busting Reels: \"Real estate mein ₹50L chahiye — MYTH.\" Hook + education. Expert positioning. Market Data Reels: \"Raipur mein yeh area mein 164% appreciation aayi\" — data visualized simply. High authority signal. Client Story Reels: 60 second client journey — \"3 saal pehle invest kiya, aaj ka update.\" Powerful social proof. Reel Formula Hook (0-3 sec): Bold text or shocking stat. Content (3-25 sec): Value delivery — tour, data, story. CTA (25-30 sec): \"Profile mein link hai ya DM karo 'Raipur' likh ke.\" Clear next step. Consistency is the Algorithm's Best Friend 3 Reels/week for 3 months = 36 Reels. Algorithm rewards consistency with organic reach. By month 3, organic views compound. One of those Reels goes viral — it's done. Equipment needed: ₹0 extra. Your phone is enough. Start filming today — imperfect content beats no content every single time.",
