      "description": "Aap ₹10,000 kharch kiya Facebook ads par. 500 log click kiye. 2 leads mile. Problem: Ad nahi — landing page hai. Yeh sabse overlooked real estate digital marketing element hai. What is a Landing Page ...",
      "content_html": "<p>Aap ₹10,000 kharch kiya Facebook ads par. 500 log click kiye. 2 leads mile. Problem: Ad nahi — landing page hai. Yeh sabse overlooked real estate digital marketing element hai.</p>\n    <h3>What is a Landing Page</h3>\n    <p>Ek single-purpose web page jahan ad se traffic jaata hai. Sirf ek kaam karta hai: Lead capture. No navigation, no distractions, no multiple offers. One message, one action.</p>\n    <h3>Anatomy of a High-Converting Property Landing Page</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Headline (top):</strong> Single biggest benefit. \"Raipur mein ₹35L se shuru — 7% rental yield ke saath\"</li>\n      <li><strong>Hero Image/Video:</strong> Best property visual or project tour video</li>\n      <li><strong>3 Bullet Benefits:</strong> Why this, why now, why us — concise</li>\n      <li><strong>Social Proof:</strong> \"200+ families ne invest kiya\" or video testimonial</li>\n      <li><strong>Lead Form:</strong> Name + Phone only. Nothing more. Less friction = more leads.</li>\n      <li><strong>CTA Button:</strong> \"Free site visit book karo\" or \"Investment guide download karo\"</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Technical Requirements</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Mobile responsive — 80% traffic is mobile</li>\n      <li>Load time under 3 seconds — every second lost = 20% fewer conversions</li>\n      <li>HTTPS secure</li>\n      <li>WhatsApp click-to-chat button visible</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>Tools to Build (Free)</h3>\n    <p>Carrd.co, Typedream, Google Sites, or Mailchimp landing pages — all free options. No coding needed. Build in 2 hours. Test and improve weekly.</p>\n    <p><strong>Your landing page is your digital salesperson. Invest ₹0 building it badly, or ₹5,000 building it right. The difference in leads over a year = 10-20x.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "Aap ₹10,000 kharch kiya Facebook ads par. 500 log click kiye. 2 leads mile. Problem: Ad nahi — landing page hai. Yeh sabse overlooked real estate digital marketing element hai. What is a Landing Page Ek single-purpose web page jahan ad se traffic jaata hai. Sirf ek kaam karta hai: Lead capture. No navigation, no distractions, no multiple offers. One message, one action. Anatomy of a High-Converting Property Landing Page Headline (top): Single biggest benefit. \"Raipur mein ₹35L se shuru — 7% rental yield ke saath\" Hero Image/Video: Best property visual or project tour video 3 Bullet Benefits: Why this, why now, why us — concise Social Proof: \"200+ families ne invest kiya\" or video testimonial Lead Form: Name + Phone only. Nothing more. Less friction = more leads. CTA Button: \"Free site visit book karo\" or \"Investment guide download karo\" Technical Requirements Mobile responsive — 80% traffic is mobile Load time under 3 seconds — every second lost = 20% fewer conversions HTTPS secure WhatsApp click-to-chat button visible Tools to Build (Free) Carrd.co, Typedream, Google Sites, or Mailchimp landing pages — all free options. No coding needed. Build in 2 hours. Test and improve weekly. Your landing page is your digital salesperson. Invest ₹0 building it badly, or ₹5,000 building it right. The difference in leads over a year = 10-20x.",
