      "description": "WhatsApp ek tool hai. Funnel ek system hai. Agar aap sirf WhatsApp use karte hain bina funnel ke — aap opportunities miss kar rahe hain. Complete WhatsApp funnel guide. What is a WhatsApp Funnel A str...",
      "content_html": "<p>WhatsApp ek tool hai. Funnel ek system hai. Agar aap sirf WhatsApp use karte hain bina funnel ke — aap opportunities miss kar rahe hain. Complete WhatsApp funnel guide.</p>\n    <h3>What is a WhatsApp Funnel</h3>\n    <p>A structured journey that takes a stranger from \"Hello\" to \"Deal Done\" entirely through WhatsApp interactions — with clear stages and triggers at each step.</p>\n    <h3>5-Stage WhatsApp Funnel for Real Estate</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Stage 1 — Awareness:</strong> Status content, group posts, forwards. Goal: Get them to DM or save your number.</li>\n      <li><strong>Stage 2 — Qualification:</strong> Automated/quick manual question: \"Kab tak property soch rahe hain? Budget?\" Tag as hot/warm/cold.</li>\n      <li><strong>Stage 3 — Education:</strong> Send curated content — area analysis, project brochure, ROI calculator. Position yourself as expert.</li>\n      <li><strong>Stage 4 — Invitation:</strong> \"Aao ek baar site dekh lete hain — main personally dikhata hoon.\" Transition to physical engagement.</li>\n      <li><strong>Stage 5 — Closure:</strong> Post-visit follow-up on WhatsApp — send closing documents, price quote, payment plan. Close via call but support via WhatsApp.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3>WhatsApp Business Setup</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Catalog: All projects listed with prices</li>\n      <li>Quick Replies: Pre-saved responses for common questions</li>\n      <li>Labels: Hot lead, Site Visit Done, Offer Made — organize your pipeline</li>\n      <li>Auto-message: \"Namaste! Main [Name] — Raipur property specialist. Aapka inquiry receive hua, main 30 min mein call karunga.\"</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><strong>A WhatsApp funnel turns a messaging app into a CRM + sales system. Setup takes 2 hours. Returns: Lifetime.</strong></p>",
      "content_text": "WhatsApp ek tool hai. Funnel ek system hai. Agar aap sirf WhatsApp use karte hain bina funnel ke — aap opportunities miss kar rahe hain. Complete WhatsApp funnel guide. What is a WhatsApp Funnel A structured journey that takes a stranger from \"Hello\" to \"Deal Done\" entirely through WhatsApp interactions — with clear stages and triggers at each step. 5-Stage WhatsApp Funnel for Real Estate Stage 1 — Awareness: Status content, group posts, forwards. Goal: Get them to DM or save your number. Stage 2 — Qualification: Automated/quick manual question: \"Kab tak property soch rahe hain? Budget?\" Tag as hot/warm/cold. Stage 3 — Education: Send curated content — area analysis, project brochure, ROI calculator. Position yourself as expert. Stage 4 — Invitation: \"Aao ek baar site dekh lete hain — main personally dikhata hoon.\" Transition to physical engagement. Stage 5 — Closure: Post-visit follow-up on WhatsApp — send closing documents, price quote, payment plan. Close via call but support via WhatsApp. WhatsApp Business Setup Catalog: All projects listed with prices Quick Replies: Pre-saved responses for common questions Labels: Hot lead, Site Visit Done, Offer Made — organize your pipeline Auto-message: \"Namaste! Main [Name] — Raipur property specialist. Aapka inquiry receive hua, main 30 min mein call karunga.\" A WhatsApp funnel turns a messaging app into a CRM + sales system. Setup takes 2 hours. Returns: Lifetime.",
